{
  "id": "adv_event_2602_01_03",
  "title": "伝えられた結果",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、ふぅ……今日はこれくらいで……\nううん、まだ、もうちょっと頑張ろうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "endTime": 15.259478378299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は試しに、既存の曲でスコアを計ってみたけど）\n（センターによって、大分、差が出ちゃったな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4507486343,
      "endTime": 24.3226757048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ちゃんとすずちゃんは、圧倒的だった。経験も）\n（そうだし、二人とも自分の強みが分かってるから……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5139459609,
      "endTime": 35.5952836988,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11372.607994000002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、渚ちゃんも来ていたんですね\n良ければ、一緒に練習しませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7865539549,
      "endTime": 42.1901581762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん！？　さっきまでお仕事だったよね？\nこんな時間から自主練するの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1901581762,
      "endTime": 49.717254733800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら渚ちゃんも、ですよ\n皆頑張っていますし、私も負けていられません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9085249899,
      "endTime": 56.7685249326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。ふふ、じゃあ私も、なおさら負けてられないね\n一緒に練習しよっか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9597951887,
      "endTime": 65.2339448927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さすがに限界～。沙季ちゃん、凄いなぁ\nBIG4になってから、ますますキレが増してるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3918746946,
      "endTime": 81.44187469459999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "同じメンバーとして、本当に心強いけど\nライバルとしては、かなりの強敵だよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6331449506,
      "endTime": 89.2067955968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとうございます。センターを務めた経験が\nない分、自分なりに技術で補おうと思っているんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3980658528,
      "endTime": 98.2580662724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんって本当に真っ直ぐだよね。特に四人体制に\nなった頃からは、そういう部分に本当に助けられてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.4493365284,
      "endTime": 109.52768163639999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "凄く真面目で、いつも周りを見てくれていて……\nどんな時でも支えてくれるけど、それだけじゃなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6999977112,
      "endTime": 120.0179792403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "努力家で、前向きで、センターに一番に立候補したり\n真っ直ぐで曲がらない、強い芯を持ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1948708529,
      "endTime": 131.2548710818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "出会った頃は、決まり事を守る人って印象だったけど\n今は、『譲れない想いを守る人』って印象かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4128008837,
      "endTime": 143.18645181600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうかもしれませんね。自分自身に誠実でいたい\n後悔しないよう、真っ直ぐに、今この時に全力をかける",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.377722072,
      "endTime": 154.160102939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それが私なりの、白石沙季の生き方なのかもしれません\nそしてその輝きで、誰かを照らせたらと心から思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.351373195,
      "endTime": 165.0314410203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、融通が利かなかったり、途中で折れちゃいそうに\nなったことは、何度もありましたけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.2227112763,
      "endTime": 171.6727113717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私もそうだった。まるで雲がかかったように\n目の前が、真っ暗になったように感じた時とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.8639816277,
      "endTime": 183.0784713738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。でも、そのたびに思うんです。それでも続けたい\nだって私は、『アイドルが好きだから』って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.2697416298,
      "endTime": 193.613324546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "私に芯があるとすれば、それかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.8045948021,
      "endTime": 197.76460084840002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "続けたい、か……。ありがとう、沙季ちゃん\n沙季ちゃんが月ストでいてくれて良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.9558711044,
      "endTime": 208.47017984299998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.6614500991,
      "endTime": 210.149323701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、こう言うのも変だけど、沙季ちゃんのセンター\n見てみたいな。きっと、誰よりも真っ直ぐで綺麗だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.340593957,
      "endTime": 220.81253476039998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "でもでも、渚ちゃんだっていいところあるよ？\nすっご～く可愛いし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.0038050165,
      "endTime": 227.3333264668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ、芽衣ちゃんっ！？　い、いつの間に！？\nていうか突然可愛いって、ど、どういうこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.5245309343,
      "endTime": 236.4890435686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……出会った頃に比べてあざとくなったというか\n可愛さが濃縮されたような感じで、正直羨ましいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.6803138246,
      "endTime": 246.88031344299998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "もし恋の時も、サキュ×まほの時も、ファンの皆さんの\n……いえ、私の心すらも、くすぐっていましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.0715836991,
      "endTime": 256.30006480099996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私そんなにあざとくないよ？　確かに琴乃ちゃんと\n一緒に、可愛いポーズの研究とかはしてたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.4913350571,
      "endTime": 264.9423551071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん！　はい、ポーズ！",
      "translations": {
